==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trichome
<hw>Trich"ome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Trichomatose</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A hair on the
surface of leaf or stem, or any modification of a hair, as a minute
scale, or star, or gland. The sporangia of ferns are believed to be of
the nature of trichomes.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Tri*chom"a*tous</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trichophore</ent>⟦br⟧
